rows.label: tlk42200111_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Lately, Talulu hasn't been able
to hide inside the barrel, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200111_03_msg0002
rows.name: It seems I've gotten fat, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to that, I'm no longer in danger of being
shipped off, but I'm completely useless
in hide-and-seek, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
So to lose weight, Talulu has been eating
a ton of Narcipear Jelly, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Mom said it's okay because you can eat a lot
and not get fat, mo!
